query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_sales,
  COUNT(DISTINCT blingOrderId) as total_orders,
  COUNT(DISTINCT productId) as products_sold,
  MIN(saleDate) as first_sale,
  MAX(saleDate) as last_sale
FROM sales;
